title: Private Mumbai Sightseeing Tour (Traveller's Choice Award Winner)

redemption.specialInstructions:
Greetings from Magical Mumbai Tours!

Thank you for selecting us for your Mumbai tours. Your tour guide and driver will be waiting for you at your hotel's car pickup and drop-off point at the scheduled time.

Should you have any trouble locating your guide, please don't hesitate to get in touch with us through a call or whatsapp on +919022801616. You can also contact us in prior for any special requirements or changes. We're dedicated to ensuring your tour is both enjoyable and unforgettable.

Please note, pickup and drop-off services are available exclusively for hotels in South and Central Mumbai. For guests staying in North Mumbai (near the Airport), an additional fee of INR 2000 is applicable, payable directly to your guide or driver at the conclusion of your tour.

Be aware that the tour's duration may range from 4 to 6 hours, depending on Mumbai's traffic conditions. We appreciate your understanding.

Thank you and best wishes,
Magical Mumbai Tours

travelerPickup.additionalInfo:
Guide & Driver will be there at your hotel's car pickup & drop point.

If you are coming from a flight then at the airport's arrival gate. 

If you are coming by a cruise then pickup from the exit gate of the port, that is called the 'Green Gate'. 

It will cost you additional INR 2000 for the pickup & drop if your hotel is at near the airport or pickup from the airport.

description: Booking our city sightseeing tour is a great way to explore and experience the vibrant city of Mumbai. Our knowledgeable and friendly tour guides, who are Mumbai University students, will take you to the top attractions of the city such as the Gateway of India, Marine Drive, Crawford Market, and many more. You'll also get to see the stunning architecture of the colonial era and learn about the history, culture, and lifestyle of Mumbai. Our tour is conducted in an air-conditioned vehicle to make your experience comfortable and convenient. By booking our city sightseeing tour, you'll have an unforgettable experience and gain a deeper appreciation for the vibrant city of Mumbai.

inclusions.otherDescription: Hotel pickup and drop-off (South & Centre Mumbai)

Vehicle: Private air-condition car.
